<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Closes 0.87 Point Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, December 20 (Xinhua) -- The price index on Amman
Financial Market closed at 170.05 Sunday, 0.87 point higher than
Saturday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 699,346 Jordanian dinars (some 979,084 U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 432,081 shares changed hand. 
</P>
