the FA Cup tie at Preston on January 4, but more likely the
following home match against Liverpool.
</P>
<P>
Adams has had a break in Florida and a special epidural
injection to try to clear up the back muscle inflammation which
has bothered him for nearly two years.
</P>
<P>
Last season, he was out from mid-December to late January, but
returned just after Arsenal had begun to turn the corner
following a dismal run of pre-Christmas form.
</P>
