<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, December 21 (Xinhua) -- Japanese automaker Honda said
Monday it is considering returning to Formula One racing in 2000,
sending it back to the world circuit after it left six years ago
because of rising costs, according to reports.
</P>
<P>
