<HEADLINE> Atletico Cali Takes Colombian League Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BOGOTA, December 20 (Xinhua) -- Atletico Cali of Colombia won
their 7th league title in a row after ending a goalless away draw
with Deportes Caldas in the second leg match on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Cali defeated Caldas 4-0 on aggregate.
</P>
<P>
During the home duel on December 16, Cali crushed Caldas 4-0.
</P>
